# Admonition Reference

## Note

N> This is a note admonition.
N> It provides additional context.

## Tip

T> This is a tip admonition.
T> It shares best practices.

## Warning

W> This is a warning admonition.
W> It alerts about potential issues.

## Important

!> This is an important admonition.
!> It highlights critical information.

## Caution

X> This is a caution admonition.
X> It warns about dangerous actions.

## Foldable Note

N>- This is a foldable note.
N> Click to expand and see details.

## Foldable Warning

W>- This is a foldable warning.
W> Contains details about a potential issue.

## Admonition with Rich Content

N> You can use **bold**, *italic*, and `code` inside admonitions.
N> Even [links](https://example.com) work here.
